description: Svetlana Alexievich's aide says the trip to Germany is not linked to the Belarus political crisis.
title: Belarus: Svetlana Alexievich, Nobel winner and opposition figure, goes to Germany
title_page: Belarus: Svetlana Alexievich, Nobel winner and opposition figure, goes to Germany - BBC News
maintext: The electoral commission says Mr Lukashenko - in power since 1994 - won a sixth term with more than 80% of votes. Last week, he was inaugurated at an unannounced ceremony in Minsk.
